# Core module context (caveman)

- Path: Modules/Core.
- Core is required by main app.
- Core is reused by all modules.
- Root rules = base law. Always follow.
- This file = extra Core law.

- Core change = big blast radius.
- Keep Core generic, stable, backward friendly.
- No module-specific business logic in Core.
- If breaking change risk: stop, warn, ask user.
